headline.main: Suicide Bomber Kills at Least 10 in Town North of Baghdad
headline.print_headline: Suicide Bomber Kills at Least 10 in Town North of Baghdad

docs.snippet: At least ten people, including four policemen, were killed by a suicide bomber in a car that targeted a checkpoint in northern Iraq on Sunday, police and medical sources said....
docs.lead_paragraph: At least ten people, including four policemen, were killed by a suicide bomber in a car that targeted a checkpoint in northern Iraq on Sunday, police and medical sources said.
